OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,FMental health wards for children and
OL,7,Fyoung people from Cumbria have been
OL,8,Frated as 'requiring improvement' by a
OL,9,Fhealth watchdog.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,12,Finspected all five of the mental
OL,13,Fhealth wards for adolescents run by
OL,14,Fthe Cumbria, Northumberland, Tyne and
OL,15,FWear NHS Foundation Trust to make
OL,16,Ftheir judgement.
