OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,FThe five wards in question are spread
OL,7,Fover two locations. Although none are
OL,8,Fsituated in Cumbria, young people from
OL,9,Fthe county are sent to them for mental
OL,10,Fhealth treatment if required.
OL,12,FThe assessment was made "in response
OL,13,Fto concerns raised about the service."
OL,15,FThe CQC found five breaches of
OL,16,Fregulation in relation to safe care
OL,17,Fand treatment, safeguarding service
OL,18,Fusers from abuse, person-centred care,
OL,19,Fstaffing and good governance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
