OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,FOut of five categories, the wards
OL,7,Freceived good ratings for patient
OL,8,Foutcomes - which was rated
OL,9,F'outstanding' in the last inspection,
OL,10,Fand for effectively meeting and
OL,11,Fresponding to patient needs.
OL,13,FThe CQC found that there was a 'high'
OL,14,Fuse of face-down and mechanical
OL,15,Frestraint in the wards, while
OL,16,Fmechanical restraint was not carried
OL,17,Fout in line with national guidance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
