OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,FIt was also found that staff had not
OL,7,Freceived all the training needed to
OL,8,Fsupport young people effectively, such
OL,9,Fas autism compliance training.
OL,11,FStaff were, however, judged by the CQC
OL,12,Fto be "caring and respectful" to
OL,13,Fpatients and provided education and a
OL,14,Frange of activities tailored to
OL,15,Fadolescents' needs.
