OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,FWhen asking young people for their
OL,7,Fthoughts, the CQC found that they
OL,8,F"mostly shared positive feedback",
OL,9,Fwhile carers' feedback was "mixed",
OL,10,Falthough they described staff as
OL,11,F"caring and responsive".
OL,13,FThe CQC has asked the Cumbria,
OL,14,FNorthumberland, Tyne and Wear NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust for an action plan to
OL,16,Frespond to these criticisms.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
