OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,FIn response, the Cumbria,
OL,7,FNorthumberland, Tyne and Wear NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust said: "I am pleased
OL,9,Fthat the report highlighted a number
OL,10,Fof positives. Young people told
OL,11,Finspectors that staff treated them
OL,12,Fwith warmth, empathy, and respect.
OL,13,FInspectors also highlighted how well
OL,14,Fstaff knew the young people in their
OL,15,Fcare. Our medicines management was
OL,16,Frated as outstanding, with inspectors
OL,17,Fpraising exemplary practice and a
OL,18,Fstrong culture of safety across our
OL,19,Fteams.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
