OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,F"Earlier in 2025 we also introduced
OL,7,Fmandatory training in how to support
OL,8,Fautistic people and people with a
OL,9,Flearning disability. We are also
OL,10,Fadding managing ligature risk to our
OL,11,Fmandatory staff training programme. We
OL,12,Fare now focussed on ensuring all staff
OL,13,Freceive this vital training as soon as
OL,14,Fpossible.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
