OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1768907051
OL,3,CMental health wards for young people
OL,4,C'require improvement'
OL,6,F"We are pleased that the report
OL,7,Frecognises that our use of restraint
OL,8,Fis reducing and we remain committed
OL,9,Fimproving this further. Staff continue
OL,10,Fto receive regular training in both
OL,11,Fsafe restraint as a last resort and in
OL,12,Fde-escalation techniques to prevent
OL,13,Fsituations from escalating. We are
OL,14,Falso reviewing and updating our
OL,15,Frestraint policy to ensure it is
OL,16,Fclearer about the exceptional
OL,17,Fcircumstances in which restraint can
OL,18,Fbe used."
